Compilation
-----------
$ mkdir build
$ cd build

$ cmake .. -DBOSP_PATH="/path/to/bosp"
or 
$ cmake .. -DBOSP_PATH="/path/to/bosp" -DMANGO_ROOT="/path/to/mango/installation"
... if you want to specify an installation path different from "/"

$ make -jX	# Replace X with number of cores for parallelize the build process

Installation
-------------------
$ sudo make install
